The paper is about improving the ranking of social media posts based on temporal signals using neural networks. This topic falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of neural networks also suggests machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper also involves data mining and analysis of social media streams, which could fall under social and information sciences (cs.SI).
